info.summary: Building blocks for REST APIs for Flask
info.html_description:
Flask-RESTy

Flask-RESTy provides building blocks for creating REST APIs with Flask, SQLAlchemy, and marshmallow.

from flask_resty import Api, GenericModelView

from . import app, models, schemas


class WidgetViewBase(GenericModelView):
    model = models.Widget
    schema = schemas.WidgetSchema()


class WidgetListView(WidgetViewBase):
    def get(self):
        return self.list()

    def post(self):
        return self.create()


class WidgetView(WidgetViewBase):
    def get(self, id):
        return self.retrieve(id)

    def patch(self, id):
        return self.update(id, partial=True)

    def delete(self, id):
        return self.destroy(id)


api = Api(app, "/api")
api.add_resource("/widgets", WidgetListView, WidgetView)
